name: Three Bean Tacos
author: B&M
summary: Lean, mean, and full of beans, these tasty tacos also feature corn and all of your favorite toppings! A delicious and flavorful taco night recipe perfect for the whole family.
ingredients: 1 (16 ounce) can B&M® Original Baked Beans
1 (15.5 ounce) can Joan of Arc® Light Red Kidney Beans, rinsed and drained
1 (15 ounce) can Joan of Arc® Black Beans, rinsed and drained
1 (11 ounce) can Green Giant® SteamCrisp® Mexicorn®
1 (1.25 ounce) package Ortega® Taco Seasoning Mix
Queso fresco, lettuce, and red onion for topping
directions: Add beans, Green Giant® SteamCrisp® Mexicorn®, 3/4 cup water, and Ortega®   to large nonstick skillet and bring to a boil over high heat
Serve in warm tortillas with your favorite taco toppings
